verbatim_text:
The Minister must, in consultation with the Committee and in accordance with the Paris Agreement... take all reasonable steps to-

(a) prepare, communicate and maintain successive NDCs that the Minister intends Fiji to achieve;
(b) pursue domestic mitigation measures, with the aim of achieving the objectives of Fiji's NDC;
(c) ... communicate a NDC every 5 years which represents a progression beyond Fiji's then current NDC and reflects Fiji's highest possible ambition...
